FBIS4-39268 "drsov109_f_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Visits Kharkov Tractor Plant Kravchuk Visits Kharkov Tractor Plant LD0606110694 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 1000 GMT 6 Jun 94 LD0606110694 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service Ukrainian BFN [Text] As we have already reported, President Leonid Kravchuk is on a working trip to Kharkov oblast today. This morning he met workers of the Kharkov tractor plant. This enterprise, one of the largest in the machine-building complex, is under threat of stoppage. Managers of agricultural machine-building enterprises supplying the Kharkov tractor plant (?also) spoke at a consultation on ways for this and other such associations to get out of the crisis situation and ways of ensuring their uninterrupted and efficient work. Ukraine's president will visit Zmiyev this afternoon. A meeting at a local vegetable-processing plant betweenthe president and his representatives in the oblast's rayons and chairmen of councils of all levels is planned.
